# Secrets
**/Secrets/*
!**/Secrets/example.*
!**/Secrets/*.example

**/.env
**/*.env
**/.env.*
**/*.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/example.env

**/*.vars
!**/*.vars.example
!**/example.vars.*

**/*.tfvars
**/*.auto.tfvars
!**/*.tfvars.example
!**/*.auto.tfvars.example

**/wireguard_configs/*
!**/wireguard_configs/example.*
!**/wireguard_configs/*.example

.DS_STORE

**/.terraform*
**/.terraform/*
**/vm_dump.md

**/output.css

**/node_modules/
**/coverage/
**/build/
**/package-lock.json
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.js

npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

.deps/
.pytest_cache/
.venv/
build/
*.egg-info/
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]